*opengl-update-2.1_pre4 (26 Jan 2005)

  26 Jan 2005; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  -files/opengl-update-2.1_pre3, +files/opengl-update-2.1_pre4,
  -opengl-update-2.1_pre3.ebuild, +opengl-update-2.1_pre4.ebuild:
  Fix bug where symlinks aren't made in lib32 if lib32 is a symlink to the
  emul dir.

*opengl-update-2.1_pre3 (25 Jan 2005)

  25 Jan 2005; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  -files/opengl-update-2.1_pre1, +files/opengl-update-2.1_pre3,
  -opengl-update-2.1_pre1.ebuild, +opengl-update-2.1_pre3.ebuild:
  Fixing bug #79539.  Fix misinstalling libglx.  Don't symlink libMesaGL.
  Remove libMesaGL on preinst.

